Package: ecoteach
Title: Educational Datasets for Ecology and Agriculture
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("W. Edwin", "Harris", , "weh9000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A collection of curated educational datasets for teaching ecology and
    agriculture concepts. Includes data on wildlife monitoring, plant treatments,
    and ecological observations with documentation and examples for educational use.
    All datasets are derived from published scientific studies and are available
    under CC0 or compatible licenses.
